ears, offering a 30% rebate on accumulated interest or \u20b910,000, whichever is higher. Property owners must pay their full outstanding dues by March 31 to avail this concession, aiming to encourage voluntary settlement and reduce long-standing liabilities.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/secunderabad-cantonment-board-launches-one-time-tax-settlement-for-property-owners/129128645?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-30354/129128645.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}